	<h1 class="title">因为玩电子设备和喝功能饮料，芬兰的年轻人睡不着了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1317/small/1317.jpg?1407490545" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">崔绮雯</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-11-24 13:33:40 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/3806/medium/3806.jpg?1436642285" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="3806" data-title="《因为玩电子设备和喝功能饮料，芬兰的年轻人睡不着了》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/3806/medium/3806.jpg?1436642285" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/3806" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
